imdb.plot outline: Leute night is an successful late night SWR1-Talk show. Sports stars, politicians, Nobel laureates, scientists or people with an interesting biography appear as guests on the show hosted by Wolfgang Heim, Stefan Siller or Katja Heijnen. Whether private, small anecdotes, stories of everyday life, future plans or current occasion - everything can be subject to the consignment.
